{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because these people were only interested-- we became, actually, friendly with the pilots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could not believe that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew about us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew why we were there, that we were inmates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were actually sympathetic to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They liked us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, after the runways.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While we were building them, they started using them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would go up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody stopped us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would go up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would come climb out of their Messerschmitt jets, and they would talk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would talk to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, we would do business with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some reason, I don't know how they did it, but some of our people in the camp got cigarettes and chocolates, candy smuggled in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know how they did it, and they would exchange them, trade them with the pilots.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They wanted-- they-- didn't-- evidently the Germany air force didn't give them enough cigarette and candy rations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would take ours, and they gave us canned foods and some of their food items.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah, that was-- they knew about us, and they-- they felt sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, I think if we had involved them in-- in-- in conversations, they-- they might have even said, listen, we-- we've-- we feel with you guys, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We think maybe the war is not going to be won.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know-- and so they treated us like normal human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had no problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These air force these pilots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were Luftwaffe soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of them, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were not-- what I'm saying, they were not hardened Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have to be members of the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were chosen because of their leadership qualities and because of their expertise in flying airplanes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In this case, these first operational jets of the whole 20th century.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
